name: setVideoQualityParameters
description:
Sets the preferences for high-quality video. (LIVE_BROADCASTING only).Deprecated:
                    Deprecated as of v2.4.0. Agora recommends using the degradationPreference parameter in the VideoEncoderConfiguration class to set the preferences for high-quality video.

parameters.preferFrameRateOverImageQuality:
Whether to prioritize smoothness or image quality.
                                true: Prioritizes smoothness.
                                false: (Default) Prioritizes the image quality.
